    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its life. The engine runs smoothly, the transmission shifts as it should, and all major mechanical systems are in solid working order. While the exterior and interior show some minor signs of regular use, such as light surface scratches and typical wear on the upholstery, the car remains clean and presentable. It is a reliable choice for anyone looking for a quality vehicle that is ready for the road with no immediate repairs needed.",
