      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 48
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Available for the discerning driver is this E36 M3, featuring the robust S50 3.0L inline-six mated to a crisp 5-speed ZF manual transmission. This example maintains its factory-spec 3.15 limited-slip differential, providing exceptional power delivery through the rear wheels. Recent preventative maintenance includes a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and a cooling system refresh with an aluminum radiator to mitigate heat soak. The chassis remains taut, benefiting from M-Technic suspension geometry and reinforced rear subframe mounts. While the exterior shows honest patina reflective of its mileage, the mechanical integrity is superlative, offering the communicative steering and balanced 50/50 weight distribution that defined the golden era of M-cars.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 48
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Used car in good condition. Well-maintained. Clean title. Reliable performance. Minimal wear.",
