    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This vehicle has been meticulously cared for and remains in impressive condition, perfect for a driver who values both performance and aesthetics. The exterior retains a deep, glossy luster, though a close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the front bumper consistent with careful highway use. Inside, the cabin is a smoke-free sanctuary; the premium leather seats are supple with only light natural creasing, and all electronic features\u2014including the high-fidelity sound system and navigation\u2014function flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is top-tier, having followed a strict manufacturer service schedule. The engine pulls smoothly, the transmission shifts with precision, and the tires have ample tread remaining. It comes complete with two sets of keys and a comprehensive folder of maintenance records, offering total peace of mind for its next owner.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
